{
  "texts": [
    "To demonstrate its performance, DeepDriveMD was applied to investigate folding of Fs-peptide and villin head piece.",
    "Compared to traditional MD-based approaches, ML based approach offers about two-fold gain in the effective performance in sampling the folded states (Lee et al. 2019).",
    "Conformational ensembles of a studied system can also be modeled directly with NNbased generative models trained on a dataset of molecular conformations from MD simulations.",
    "Recently, idpGAN was developed to generate physically realistic conformational ensembles of proteins.",
    "For this purpose, a conditional generative adversarial network (GAN) was used, whose generator is based on a transformer architecture and uses the peptide sequence as a condition."
  ]
}